@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Add Temperature & Humidity Reading
POST {{baseUrl}}/reading
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "temperature": 22.5,
  "humidity": 55
}

### Add Another Reading (Higher Temperature)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reading
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "temperature": 25.3,
  "humidity": 48
}

### Add Multiple Readings for Testing
POST {{baseUrl}}/reading
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "temperature": 20.1,
  "humidity": 60
}

### Get All Readings (Last 24 Hours)
GET {{baseUrl}}/readings?hours=24

### Get Readings (Last 6 Hours)
GET {{baseUrl}}/readings?hours=6

### Get Readings (Last 1 Hour)
GET {{baseUrl}}/readings?hours=1

### Get Analysis (Last 24 Hours)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analysis?hours=24

### Get Analysis (Last 7 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analysis?hours=168

### Get Analysis (Last 6 Hours)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analysis?hours=6

### View Interactive Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard

